        <p>When I’m not becoming one with machine, you’ll find me at the gym practicing the art of Muay Thai. I briefly competed, now I dedicate my energy to being what they call a "pad-man" and instructor. Helping my teammates become champions has been incredibly rewarding and seeing them at their best and perhaps their worst has taught me a lot about resilience and teamwork to say the least.
